                  "KINDT"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The 24-O secondary beam was produced via",
                "projectile fragmentation of a 48Ca beam at 1A GeV on",
                "a Be target placed at the entrance of the FRS.The",
                "nuclei produced were then separated and identified",
                "event by event using the first half of the FRS, with",
                "the magnetic rigidity, energy loss and time-of- flight",
                "information."
              ]
            }
